also become unlucky.

65
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:31,240
Maybe you should stay away from me,

66
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,250
or you'll be unlucky too.

67
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:33,560
It's fine.

68
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:36,160
A real man stands tall and strong.

69
