are truly extraordinary.

95
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:16,280
You were born unlucky,

96
00:05:16,280 --> 00:05:17,080
but my brother

97
00:05:17,080 --> 00:05:19,480
is the bringer of good fortune
in Yongzhou.

98
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:21,240
Really?

99
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:21,960
Yes.

100
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,440
