115
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:58,720
We can share some of his luck

116
00:05:58,720 --> 00:06:00,090
and it'll counteract our bad luck.

117
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,080
Alright.

118
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,040
